<materialsCitation id="3B45515BF764B125B182FA8731914504" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3766756404" collectingDate="1854-06-24" collectingDateMax="1854-07-20" collectingDateMin="1854-06-24" collectionCode="TYPE" country="South Africa" county="Swakop River" location="Wahlberg" municipality="Wahlberg's" pageId="17" pageNumber="538" specimenCount="2" typeStatus="lectotype">
<collectionCode id="ED3CC3C3F764B125B182FA8732C246D2" box="[199,251,1400,1426]" pageId="17" pageNumber="538">TYPE</collectionCode>
MATERIAL: 
<location id="8EF20DDDF764B125B030FA8733D846D0" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:0384EA10F764B125B1D2FB3C311044EC:8EF20DDDF764B125B030FA8733D846D0" box="[373,481,1400,1426]" country="South Africa" county="Swakop River" municipality="Wahlberg's" name="Wahlberg" pageId="17" pageNumber="538">Wahlberg</location>
in his original description (1855: 213) gave data for both male and female. 
<location id="8EF20DDDF764B125B463FA8737A546D0" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:0384EA10F764B125B1D2FB3C311044EC:8EF20DDDF764B125B463FA8737A546D0" box="[1318,1436,1400,1426]" country="South Africa" county="Swakop River" municipality="Wahlberg's" name="According" pageId="17" pageNumber="538">According</location>
to 
<location id="8EF20DDDF764B125B1F1FA63330E46F4" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:0384EA10F764B125B1D2FB3C311044EC:8EF20DDDF764B125B1F1FA63330E46F4" box="[180,311,1436,1462]" country="South Africa" county="Swakop River" municipality="Wahlberg's" name="Sundevall's" pageId="17" pageNumber="538">Sundevall’s</location>
manuscript acquisition catalogue 
<specimenCount id="9D2B908FF764B125B3F0FA63315146F4" box="[693,872,1436,1462]" pageId="17" pageNumber="538" type="generic">three specimens</specimenCount>
were received from 
<collectingCountry id="F33A1B96F764B125B50AFA6336E746F4" box="[1103,1246,1436,1462]" name="South Africa" pageId="17" pageNumber="538">South Africa</collectingCountry>
after 
<collectingMunicipality id="6BF6C17CF764B125B45BFA6337A546F4" box="[1310,1436,1436,1462]" pageId="17" pageNumber="538">Wahlberg’s</collectingMunicipality>
death. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFBC26F7F764B125B1A6FA3F33CF4699" author="Gyldenstolpe, N." box="[227,502,1472,1499]" pageId="17" pageNumber="538" pagination="1 - 116" refId="ref28755" refString="Gyldenstolpe, N. (1926) Types of birds in the Royal Natural History Museum in Stockholm. Arkiv f or Zoologi, 19, 1 - 116." type="journal article" year="1926">Gyldenstolpe (1926: 26)</bibRefCitation>
referred to NRM 569772 [11745] as a “type”, which we treat as a 
<typeStatus id="5496E5A4F764B125B5AFFA3F37684698" box="[1258,1361,1472,1498]" pageId="17" pageNumber="538">lectotype</typeStatus>
designation of this study skin of a male collected 
<date id="FF937DC6F764B125B3CDFA1B312746BD" box="[648,798,1508,1535]" pageId="17" pageNumber="538" value="1854-06-24">
<collectingDate id="EFD7842EF764B125B3CDFA1B312746BD" box="[648,798,1508,1535]" pageId="17" pageNumber="538" value="1854-06-24">
24 June 
<quantity id="4CD5F6E3F764B125B3A3FA1B312746BD" box="[742,798,1508,1535]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.70916" pageId="17" pageNumber="538" unit="in" value="1854.0">1854</quantity>
</collectingDate>
</date>
in sand desert 
<locationDeviation id="9A204224F764B125B282FA1B32FA4560" firstLocation="Kuiseb River" pageId="17" pageNumber="538" secondLocation="Swakop River. The">between Kuiseb River and Swakop River. The</locationDeviation>
<specimenCount id="9D2B908FF764B125B18CF9F733A24560" box="[201,411,1544,1570]" pageId="17" pageNumber="538" type="generic" typeStatus="paralectotypes">two paralectotypes</specimenCount>
are: NRM 90200072 [11744], a male with the same data as the lectotype, and NRM 534747 [11746], a mounted female collected 
<date id="FF937DC6F764B125B37DF9D330F04505" box="[568,713,1580,1607]" pageId="17" pageNumber="538" value="1854-07-20">
<collectingDate id="EFD7842EF764B125B37DF9D330F04505" box="[568,713,1580,1607]" pageId="17" pageNumber="538" value="1854-07-20">20 July 1854</collectingDate>
</date>
near 
<collectingCounty id="62F3238AF764B125B242F9D331914504" box="[775,936,1580,1606]" pageId="17" pageNumber="538">Swakop River</collectingCounty>
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B925B06F764B125B182F9AF362E4528" blockId="17.[151,1437,1292,1966]" box="[199,1047,1616,1642]" pageId="17" pageNumber="538">
